{"tid":1118543,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個\"動保撚\"奇怪邏輯","createTime":"2019-04-21T13:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T04:18:43.000Z","uid":109743,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"54cec6264cc78aef17b5f846dc747f2a294def07","tid":1118543,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:05:15.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔知應唔應該叫佢地動保撚<br />\n佢地唔應該叫動保撚，應該叫狗保撚/貓保撚<br />\n因為我見果幾個根本唔係愛護動物,佢地只係愛貓狗<br />\n<br />\n1. 為左救疑似被&quot;蟒蛇&quot;吞落肚既狗BB而殺蛇，看到滿肚的狗B屍體，無懼觸犯&quot;野生動物保護條例&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2239237/%E3%80%90%E9%80%9F%E6%95%91%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%A9%E3%80%91%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E7%8B%97B%20%E8%A2%AB%E9%B7%B9%E7%8D%B5%E6%AE%BA%20%E4%B8%83%E9%9A%BB%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%9B%E9%9A%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2239237%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%259F%25E6%2595%2591%25E6%25AF%259B%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E7%258B%2597B%2520%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25B7%25B9%25E7%258D%25B5%25E6%25AE%25BA%2520%25E4%25B8%2583%25E9%259A%25BB%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%259B%25E9%259A%25BB&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=c52a52d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2239237/%E3%80%90%E9%80%9F%E6%95%91%E6%AF%9B%E5%AD%A9%E3%80%91%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E7%8B%97B%20%E8%A2%AB%E9%B7%B9%E7%8D%B5%E6%AE%BA%20%E4%B8%83%E9%9A%BB%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%9B%E9%9A%BB</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 貓殺野鳥就係弱肉強食，蛇殺貓就係殘忍，要捉走條蛇，明明郊區係蛇既屋企，貓係郊區入侵者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.非常支持漁護署殺野豬，佢既原因係野豬搞到郊區d流浪貓狗無啖好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.有個餵流浪貓阿姐會帶打火機上山，原因係佢話會見一個蜘蛛網燒一個，連蜘蛛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為蜘蛛網會搞到d流浪貓狗唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n5.漁護署Facebook教生態知識，佢就不斷狙擊漁護署捉流浪貓狗，罵漁護署唔識生態，破壞生態平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (真係唔知邊個唔識生態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n仲有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4a43bf267961e3083307bcd5c3fb51cdf88f2c","tid":1118543,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"你自己都識講狗保撚/貓保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed70b6d7a11f25007f1e33d237fa1786ed66e541","tid":1118543,"uid":42982,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"食狗肉係冷血，但食魚刺身無問題"},{"pid":"45b19f4e7182c6012c9398c24b40ede3607b2016","tid":1118543,"uid":129506,"like":8,"dislike":21,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"ed70b6d7a11f25007f1e33d237fa1786ed66e541","tid":1118543,"uid":42982,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"食狗肉係冷血，但食魚刺身無問題"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"哩個唔關動保撚事啦，只係大眾價值觀係狗=朋友<br />\n唔洗問點解咁唔公平，世界就係唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858d67ad0ca1d3fc6c898b9bb9c226dd73caef58","tid":1118543,"uid":192491,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"45b19f4e7182c6012c9398c24b40ede3607b2016","tid":1118543,"uid":129506,"like":8,"dislike":21,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"ed70b6d7a11f25007f1e33d237fa1786ed66e541","tid":1118543,"uid":42982,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"食狗肉係冷血，但食魚刺身無問題"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"哩個唔關動保撚事啦，只係大眾價值觀係狗=朋友<br />\n唔洗問點解咁唔公平，世界就係唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:27:36.000Z","msg":"咁樣此post已完"},{"pid":"68c8cc5cba28a49265368038f3ccaa37720d4031","tid":1118543,"uid":39668,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"45b19f4e7182c6012c9398c24b40ede3607b2016","tid":1118543,"uid":129506,"like":8,"dislike":21,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"ed70b6d7a11f25007f1e33d237fa1786ed66e541","tid":1118543,"uid":42982,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"食狗肉係冷血，但食魚刺身無問題"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"哩個唔關動保撚事啦，只係大眾價值觀係狗=朋友<br />\n唔洗問點解咁唔公平，世界就係唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:55:52.000Z","msg":"係呀殺狗殺貓殺雀就慘慘豬<br />\n牛羊馬魚全部就抵死既<br />\n<br />\n最博愛啦滿意啦?"},{"pid":"5976b61780b66884692b96fede736af47e930cbb","tid":1118543,"uid":228223,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"45b19f4e7182c6012c9398c24b40ede3607b2016","tid":1118543,"uid":129506,"like":8,"dislike":21,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"ed70b6d7a11f25007f1e33d237fa1786ed66e541","tid":1118543,"uid":42982,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"食狗肉係冷血，但食魚刺身無問題"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"哩個唔關動保撚事啦，只係大眾價值觀係狗=朋友<br />\n唔洗問點解咁唔公平，世界就係唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"親疏有別就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8a971e21ab3d3475d180dfd49a4d2be15e8317","tid":1118543,"uid":55493,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"所有動物生來平等，但有些動物比其他動物更平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n動物保護，甚至生態保育嘅正當性向來都係依賴於人類嘅超然，超然而萬物，而唔係將人同動物放喺同等位置、同水平嚟考量，如果唔係超然又憑咩講保護？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係人要動物點就點，動物冇權揀被點對待，所以不論人嘅選擇係咩都係可以自圓其說，例如有人要捉隻獅子返去「保護」，隻獅子反抗只會畀人用麻醉針射，而唔會得到意願上嘅尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人嘅思路就係各種動物嘅生死都係由最優秀（有能力）嘅物種，即係人，控制。<br />\n<br />\n所謂動保撚嘅宗旨唔係維持生態自然，而係保障部分動物嘅超然地位，超然自然唔係自然原貌，正如狼食羊係應份，唔通叫狼食草咩，但係睇下套喜羊羊，哈哈，例如貓被人類賦與高於老鼠嘅地位，呢種超然都係依賴於人嘅超然<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人有生殺大權，呢點不論係認為某啲動物比其他動物更有生存權利嘅人，或者認為人唔應該干預自然界原本生態嘅人都會某程度上認可。<br />\n<br />\n前者好易理解，例如蛇吞貓要剖蛇救貓，或者瀕臨絕種嘅動物應該得到特別對待都係前者。<br />\n<br />\n至於後者較難理解，點解唔干涉都係控制生死呢？因為有能力，假如有個雨林有動物就嚟絕種，你有能力救佢，你選擇唔救，噉同你選擇殺佢又有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n當然仲有一種強調自己係「平衡生態，還原生態」嘅主張，於我所見，都係同樣自命有能力控制生態發展啦。<br />\n<br />\n只要人依然超然，噉不論點樣看待自然界嘅行為都會有充分理據支撐，所以唔洗認真思考所謂動保撚嘅邏輯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1abb1fb503d04413ea8fd72d58c7d8f6cdb6c79","tid":1118543,"uid":132326,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T15:49:24.000Z","msg":"就係偏愛貓狗 吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc03b7ed263162c5f3a4cffcf195bbbb795b6b9a","tid":1118543,"uid":129087,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T23:34:24.000Z","msg":"偏愛唔緊要 但好心你班友仔就唔好搶道德高地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大大聲認左佢咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5922878dfcec0435581c148a3e249ad4e8e5460","tid":1118543,"uid":47723,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T23:59:16.000Z","msg":"貓狗係佢哋眼中先係動物 <br />\n其他垃圾都不如"},{"pid":"0516f4c626daa8a0c192a6c421514c09ab053fd4","tid":1118543,"uid":109743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5922878dfcec0435581c148a3e249ad4e8e5460","tid":1118543,"uid":47723,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T23:59:16.000Z","msg":"貓狗係佢哋眼中先係動物 <br />\n其他垃圾都不如"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"Sad but true"},{"pid":"9ca3078fdf1082d861d92b93cfacff185e00c894","tid":1118543,"uid":109435,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:06:04.000Z","msg":"有好多人鐘意貓狗(特別係貓)，好似鐘意到癲左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下fb啲group就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7548778b02ff794e00ce732e9ab1ec42afe944b9","tid":1118543,"uid":109743,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9ca3078fdf1082d861d92b93cfacff185e00c894","tid":1118543,"uid":109435,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:06:04.000Z","msg":"有好多人鐘意貓狗(特別係貓)，好似鐘意到癲左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇下fb啲group就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"我都鐘意貓，但會理性<br />\n<br />\n我見好多人愛貓狗愛到唔理性，愛到破壞其他生物，夾硬話流浪貓狗係生態大自然物種，我覺得好噁心"},{"pid":"e26aadf9ef64243f5763f28789cda5081067d414","tid":1118543,"uid":216477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecea661019a3c7130214d79ace544c12a9de4660","tid":1118543,"uid":202539,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79e1706a9acb5e21a80bb75dd4a6225f5212aa18","tid":1118543,"uid":54437,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e26aadf9ef64243f5763f28789cda5081067d414","tid":1118543,"uid":216477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5976b61780b66884692b96fede736af47e930cbb","tid":1118543,"uid":228223,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"45b19f4e7182c6012c9398c24b40ede3607b2016","tid":1118543,"uid":129506,"like":8,"dislike":21,"score":-13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"哩個唔關動保撚事啦，只係大眾價值觀係狗=朋友<br />\n唔洗問點解咁唔公平，世界就係唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"親疏有別就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"其實好合理<br />\n鍾意嘅就保<br />\n唔鐘意嘅就wfc"},{"pid":"9f38c68b969ffe310c892dc1effb20f5a37dae3b","tid":1118543,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:36:32.000Z","msg":"有冇人又討論狗肉節"},{"pid":"52e9250feef9a4b7c978ea9e18c3359a4de5edea","tid":1118543,"uid":216477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6cf6283e35e794318e45d6580497b10eb37a61e","tid":1118543,"uid":109743,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:07:58.000Z","msg":"我見有人淨係識逐個留言負評，唔敢出嚟講下？"},{"pid":"66a91b327fc79ec74f279c241e7a3450d6c1d489","tid":1118543,"uid":13257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"基本上你接受倒貓狗比其他動物高一級，就一切都無問題。"},{"pid":"4f6910b3dc557ad4405e0896243c725ce03b5694","tid":1118543,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T03:03:27.000Z","msg":"19才子都咁講:你唔食貓食狗，你就唔係完整中國人"},{"pid":"1157140b90014c80ccfbd4d68e0d42ac605bfb48","tid":1118543,"uid":109743,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7c4a43bf267961e3083307bcd5c3fb51cdf88f2c","tid":1118543,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"你自己都識講狗保撚/貓保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"問題係好多狗保撚/貓保撚都係以動保撚自居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話自己愛動物，但其實只愛貓狗"},{"pid":"65eaba6caae7db291d43cb1748ca9a9db7005445","tid":1118543,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1157140b90014c80ccfbd4d68e0d42ac605bfb48","tid":1118543,"uid":109743,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7c4a43bf267961e3083307bcd5c3fb51cdf88f2c","tid":1118543,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"你自己都識講狗保撚/貓保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"問題係好多狗保撚/貓保撚都係以動保撚自居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話自己愛動物，但其實只愛貓狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T09:20:41.000Z","msg":"唔知野狗咬死野貓, 班動保撚會點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d64f2673c5d818b97c5aa8d4f8e988fe5797352","tid":1118543,"uid":193209,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T10:26:01.000Z","msg":"隻狗喺條街屙尿，拎支水&rdquo;茲&rdquo;就當清潔咗"}]}